        <updateDate>2007-11-07T21:24:30Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p>Child Care Family Tax Relief Act of 2007 - Amends the Internal Revenue Code to: (1) increase the rate of the tax credit for expenses for household and dependent care services; and (2) allow an inflation adjustment after 2007 to the adjusted gross income limitation applicable to such credit. Makes such increased tax credit permanent. </p>]]></text>
      </summary>
